elements.contents:
Share information
Cube Storage Pioneers

Little Robots, Big Business

Since its inception in 1996, AutoStore™ has worked to improve warehouse efficiency. Today, the company’s key value proposition is to deliver an easy-to-use software powered cubic automatic storage and retrieval ecosystem.

The AutoStore solution is modular and flexible, and can automate any warehouse. The system offers a superior customer value proposition across operating metrics, ESG scores, and customer economics.
‍

View video to learn more

elements.contents:
Our Legacy

The Cube Storage Pioneers

elements.title: Electriquette (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that the Electriquette (example pictured) was an electric wicker vehicle that could be rented at the 1915 Panama–California Exposition?

elements.title: Tokamak de Fontenay-aux-Roses (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that shortly after it was completed, the Tokamak de Fontenay-aux-Roses burned a hole through itself in a plasma disruption?

elements.title: Józef Ignacy Kraszewski (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that 19th-century Polish writer Józef Ignacy Kraszewski authored hundreds of works, including more than 200 novels?

elements.title: abortion in Benin (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that the legalization of abortion in Benin was supported by two members of the cabinet who had both worked as gynecologists?

elements.title: Alex Chilowicz (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that in December 2023, former Major League Soccer referee Alex Chilowicz began officiating in the English Football League after relocating to England?

elements.title: Marmelada de Santa Luzia (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that many producers of Marmelada de Santa Luzia, a variety of quince cheese, are descendants of quilombolas?

elements.title: Nathaniel Coe (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that Nathaniel Coe declined nomination to the United States Senate, instead choosing to serve as an inspector for the United States Postal Service?

elements.title: Cosmetic Playlover (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that Sachi Narashima came up with the idea for the manga Cosmetic Playlover after her friend, who worked as a beauty consultant, mentioned that there were male beauty consultants?

elements.title: Mary Jo West (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that Mary Jo West compared working in network TV news to learning that Santa Claus is just an ordinary man?
